===Show preview===  
Second, you should always use the '''[[Help:Show preview|Show preview]]''' button. After you have entered a change in the edit box, click the <!-- Can someone put an actual button here to make things clear to newusers? -->'''{{Mediawiki:Showpreview}}''' button instead of '''Save page'''. This lets you see what the page will look like after your edit, ''before'' you actually save. We all make mistakes; this feature helps you catch them before other people see them. Using '''{{Mediawiki:Showpreview}}''' before saving also lets you try format changes and other edits without cluttering up the [[Help:Page history|page history]].
