==Protected pages==
Some pages are [[WP:Protection policy|protected from editing]]. These pages have a <tt>View source</tt> tab instead of an <tt>Edit</tt> tab. You can still edit these pages indirectly, by submitting an "[[Wikipedia:Edit requests|edit request]]"&nbsp;– a user with the ability to edit the protected page will respond to your request. You can submit a request by clicking on the <tt>View source</tt> tab on that page and using the "Submit an edit request" link at the bottom right.

